# BuildKit per-Dockerfile ignore (docker >= 23 with BuildKit reads
# `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore` next to the -f Dockerfile). The build needs the
# workspace manifests, Cargo.lock, rust-toolchain.toml, and crates/ — keep the
# multi-gigabyte build artifacts and the app/marketing trees out of the context.
target
.git
node_modules
apps
coverage
marketing
public
docs
.beads
